### 13. REFRESH TOKEN
# Utiliza las cookies automáticamente configuradas
POST {{back_cabs_HostAddress}}/api/Auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 14. LOGOUT
POST {{back_cabs_HostAddress}}/api/Auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

